"No files were uploaded. Please check file type and size limits and try again."
msgstr ""
"No se cargaron archivos. Verifique los límites de tamaño y tipo de archivo e "
"inténtelo nuevamente."

#. translators: %1$d: rejected videos count, %2$d: max upload size in MB
#: guest-upload-vault/includes/class-guest-upload-vault-plugin.php:1080
