#: guest-upload-vault/templates/frontend-upload.php:319
msgid ""
"On iPhone/Android you can choose camera, photo library/gallery, or files."
msgstr ""
"En iPhone/Android puedes elegir cámara, biblioteca/galería de fotos o "
